# Redirect Clerk auth flows from apex to app subdomain.
# Required because Clerk's proxy URL is on the apex (https://aloomii.com/__clerk),
# so OAuth callbacks land on aloomii.com after sign-in. The portal lives on
# app.aloomii.com, so we forward auth-related paths there.
#
# Status 302 (temporary) so browsers don't cache and we can change later.
# Order matters: more specific paths first, then catch-alls.
# DO NOT redirect /__clerk/* — the Pages Function in functions/__clerk handles it.

/sign-in              https://app.aloomii.com/sign-in              302
/sign-in/*            https://app.aloomii.com/sign-in/:splat       302
/sign-up              https://app.aloomii.com/sign-up              302
/sign-up/*            https://app.aloomii.com/sign-up/:splat       302
/sso-callback         https://app.aloomii.com/sso-callback         302
/sso-callback/*       https://app.aloomii.com/sso-callback/:splat  302
/user                 https://app.aloomii.com/user                 302
/user/*               https://app.aloomii.com/user/:splat          302
/app                  https://app.aloomii.com/app                  302
/app/*                https://app.aloomii.com/app/:splat           302
